Title: On the finiteness of the noncommutative supersymmetric  Maxwell-Chern-Simons theory
Authors: A. F. Ferrari and M. Gomes and J. R. Nascimento and A. Yu. Petrov and A. J. da Silva and E. O. Silva
Abstract: Within the superfield approach, we prove the absence of UV/IR mixing in the three-dimensional noncommutative supersymmetric Maxwell-Chern-Simons theory at any loop order and demonstrate its finiteness in one, three and higher loop orders.
